Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那麼龐大的神社
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:21.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非得要我一個人來掃除呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點掃除完  到行人大人那裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:30.20,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（別給我擅自把它吃掉  姐）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:28.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別給我擅自把它吃掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.10,0:00:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經吃掉了——！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:15.00,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑吧  擺脫吧  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,海龍神社…真的是在足夠高的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧  行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我把這些蘿蔔給千鶴小姐送去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人就先在這裡休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡沒事了  快下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但你是特意來見我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目標是我的妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼妹妹的…話說  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但那孩子不在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一直在找
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  麻知姐是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧  行人不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知姐是綾音的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  作為姐姐的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼是妻子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:28.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴小姐不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽的話在的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概在廚房關著門而沒有聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為在做紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅豆大福？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.66,0:03:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴小姐做的紅豆大福  非常好吃的哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如此  富有彈性的皮  味道濃郁的餡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  口水流下來了…口水…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  去把綾音找來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.24,0:03:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不擇手段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:03:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音她又做什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了的話就給你媽媽特製的這軟呼呼的紅豆大福二十個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅豆大福  二十個？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯  無論如何我都會去找的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  鈴拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接受尋找綾音這種事  沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可認為沒那麼容易就找出來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音的胸部是洗衣板～！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,洗衣板…洗衣板…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰～是洗衣板啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害  從對面馬上就跑過來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:05:00.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在發育中  絕對不是洗衣板的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音啾…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  不知道  不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,召喚作戰大成功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音  現在是不會下手的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點鑽進這麻袋裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐唆使的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為  抓住綾音的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以得到二十個紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可和麻知姐約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  真沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你這不是犯罪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:31.97,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼感覺和平時相反了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.67,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情也不打招呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:34.94,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鏘～紅豆大福！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紋次郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅豆大福逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼連我都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴那傢伙還真拼命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那傢伙一旦關係到甜品的話就性情大變了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是  我家媽媽做的秘傳紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是鈴最愛中的最愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被紅豆大福所收買的鈴簡直就是解開鎖鏈的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小心點  行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不知道發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但坦誠的向麻知道歉怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,道歉也沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人不知道姐姐大人真正的可怕之處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,單單是回憶就很恐懼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要成為姐姐的實驗體要有這樣差點被殺死的遭遇…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  姐姐大人  不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音  別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓綾音怕成這樣  麻知究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅豆大福找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點  來我這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:59.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅豆大福…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來做個交易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能找出我姐姐的弱點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給你比姐姐多十個  也就是三十個紅豆大福  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.33,0:07:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個怎麼說都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三十個？接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼簡單就被收買了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知姐的弱點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼麻知姐本人最清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去問問看～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情不可能會告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但鈴去問的話  會有意外的收穫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我們這邊也去打聽姐姐的弱點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正結果都能預料了  放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結果  什麼結果？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.82,0:07:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐頭的弱點？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,外人也許會比家裡人更加容易注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,凜知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐頭的弱點嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:08:01.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  確實以前說過  討厭南邊田野裡的大牛蛙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等著吧  大牛蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  記得大牛蛙會有把靠近周圍的人都吞噬的屬性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心點的話 會很危險…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你解釋的也太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:27.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知小姐所討厭的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能回想起什麼姐姐的弱點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也沒期待你這小鬼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別叫我小鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是弱點不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她以前捉弄我  看我不會吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就感覺到無聊  那種小事倒是有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐總是拿別人的反映作為取樂的物件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說無論怎麼捉弄  只要我沒反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不會繼續下去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:08:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵呵呵  姐姐  既不痛也不癢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～  不管是誰也好  快來阻止她！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  如果我沒反應的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐一定會更加兇暴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結果還是沒找到姐姐的一擊致命的弱點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  還是在下手之前就此作罷怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了  綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知姐的弱點知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  偉大  我沒期待錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「心臟被刀或矢所刺到就會死」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  那就是說你的心臟被什麼刺到就不會死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是  太不甘心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就沒有其他的什麼嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:10:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道就沒有能讓那過氣的老婆婆一擊致命的弱點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,過氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  姐姐已經18歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全是個過氣過了妙齡的老女人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（過氣）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.62,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（老女人）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  這樣說的話  麻知姐她會失落的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然背叛我了  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把姐姐大人帶過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為快點讓你們見面和好才對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  原來是這樣想的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  如果帶她來綾音這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻知姐說她就給我50個紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是紅豆大福嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了  麻知
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看姐姐這失落的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說姐姐很在意自己的年齡問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,驚！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈  終於找到姐姐的弱點了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.94,0:11:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老相  老婆婆  過氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了這一時刻  我才把稻草人一直藏著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話  你就什麼都做不了哦  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老相  老相～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,式神召喚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老相  老相～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然還有那種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人  饒恕我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不～要～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前面的路會變窄了  小心點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  鈴才要小心腳下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經習慣這路…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:11:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:06.59,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,吃驚吧  惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,摔到屁股了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是因為昨天下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路變得容易滑倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.65,0:12:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  要人小心點的本人卻自己掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.61,0:12:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  居然取笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  抱歉  真沒受傷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  只是擦到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  感覺有什麼撞到屁股了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀  地藏菩薩被撞壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼會在這麼偏僻的角落裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把地藏菩薩撞壞了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會被詛咒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  就這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能會沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個地藏菩薩可不是普通的地藏菩薩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一百年前有個幹盡壞事的惡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是當時巫女封印在這裡  並且製成了石像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  並不是完全沒事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那麼在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣  這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看  恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我屁股腫了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要特意讓我看了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我自己又看不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊  行人一點都不害怕幽靈或妖怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.10,0:14:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事都是因為害怕  所以才會把虛無的東西看成幽靈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再說我對那些鬼怪之類的不科學的東西沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只相信自己所見的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  鈴把那地藏菩薩給…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:34.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  凜你們也知道啊  那個傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是島上七大不可思議之一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  這樣看上去鈴就像是妖怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚開始就一直這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,半夜吵鬧不聽  差點被她掐死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全睡眠不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:55.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話  來我家留宿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  我家的被子可是很軟的  公子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我家有西洋的床哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是雙人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看著如此害怕的鈴  不做些什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的確有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  如果真的被惡靈附身的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  連千影和凜都相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…因為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從小時候就聽說過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊  所謂傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了不讓小孩接近危險的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才編造出來的大人的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說  騙小孩的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說我「小孩」～！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎在說夢話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總而言之呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼鬼魂  妖怪  詛咒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可能存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  鈴也別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在鈴背後有白色的手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.28,0:16:06.63,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  行人  振作一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:15:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒有這麼捉弄鈴了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  鈴被附身也是事實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.06,0:16:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我能看到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憑著這繼承巫女之血的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到附在鈴背後惡靈的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:23.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦被附身的話  無論何時何地都會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最後把鈴的靈魂拖入冥府為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  不要說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了不要這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  綾音那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是越來越嚴重了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點出來吧  吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過說起來  真意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴也有害怕的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.38,0:17:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了今晚能心情舒適的睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再嚇一嚇鈴好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是為什麼這樣害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本從小開始就比別人更害怕幽靈之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上一個人不敢在黑暗的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人生活後  稍微能適應了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但一旦聽到可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕的話就會覺得很悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每當我害怕的時候  一直都是媽媽安慰著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  一旦害怕  就會回憶起媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:18:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕和悲傷交織在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事  不是還有我在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也許不能像鈴的媽媽那樣溫柔的安慰你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但在當鈴感到害怕  寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:22.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都會在你身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難得同情你  想老實的回去的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.29,0:18:43.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是兩個人的氣氛不錯  感覺真討厭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是稍微嚇她一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  面具放在哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:49.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:50.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出…出現了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.86,0:19:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是來嚇唬鈴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真閒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛…剛才  在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有惡靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人大人  我…好害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被附身了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…惡靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  那種東西像平常那樣扔飛不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這時候  才是受過除靈訓練的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天才美少女巫女綾音的出場！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了  行人一個人也好快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這樣說也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別舔我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑也是要有程度的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  不害怕嗎  那是妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.30,0:20:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:37.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這世界上像幽靈妖怪這樣不科學的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是絕對不存在的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:41.67,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（存在被完全否定）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因為大家認定它是惡靈妖怪什麼的才害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,它才會放肆惡作劇的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.43,0:20:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是什麼惡靈  我會和大家說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以再惡作劇了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:01.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  好  你也很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也算是除靈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,消…消失了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙走的好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說那傢伙根本沒有腳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是妖怪會是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會是白熊吧
